definitions.definition: An anonymous person , traditionally especially a published author but now especially an internet rando .

subdefinitions.definition: An anonymous poster ( “ person who contributes a note, message, etc ” ) . A participant in an online site, such as a forum or an imageboard, without an account, or who posts without identifying themselves, or hidden behind a pseudonym .

definitions.definition: A work with an unknown author.

main_definition: An anonymous person , traditionally especially a published author but now especially an internet rando .
secondary_definitions: A work with an unknown author.
